    '                                        <input id="new-referral-delay-sec" type="number" min="0" value="${task?.config?.referralDelay ? Math.floor(task?.config?.referralDelay / 1000) % 60 : 0}" class="time-input" placeholder="0">',
    '                                        <span class="time-label">秒</span>',
    '                                    </div>',
    '                                    <div class="time-input-group">',
    '                                        <input id="new-referral-delay-min" type="number" min="0" value="${task?.config?.referralDelay ? Math.floor(task?.config?.referralDelay / 60000) % 60 : 0}" class="time-input" placeholder="0">',
    '                                        <span class="time-label">分钟</span>',
    '                                    </div>',
    '                                    <div class="time-input-group">',
    '                                        <input id="new-referral-delay-hours" type="number" min="0" value="${task?.config?.referralDelay ? Math.floor(task?.config?.referralDelay / 3600000) % 24 : 0}" class="time-input" placeholder="0">',
    '                                        <span class="time-label">小时</span>',
    '                                    </div>',
    '                                    <div class="time-input-group">',
    '                                        <input id="new-referral-delay-days" type="number" min="0" value="${task?.config?.referralDelay ? Math.floor(task?.config?.referralDelay / 86400000) : 0}" class="time-input" placeholder="0">',
    '                                        <span class="time-label">天</span>',
    '                                    </div>',
    '                                </div>',
    '                                <div class="text-xs text-slate-400 text-center mt-1">',
    '                                    总间隔: <span class="text-emerald-400">${task?.config?.referralDelay ? formatMsDelay(task?.config?.referralDelay) : \'0秒\'}</span>',
    '                                </div>',
    '                                <div id="new-referral-delay-hint" class="text-xs mt-1 p-2 rounded-lg ${task?.config?.referralProxyEnabled ? \'bg-cyan-900/30 border border-cyan-500/30\' : \'bg-amber-900/30 border border-amber-500/30\'}">${task?.config?.referralProxyEnabled ? \'<span class="text-cyan-300"><i class="fas fa-random mr-1"></i>已开启IP轮换：无需设置注册间隔，代理获取/验证/连接本身需要时间，会自动连续注册</span>\' : \'<span class="text-amber-300"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle mr-1"></i>未开启IP轮换：所有注册用同一IP，间隔必须设5分钟以上，否则会被限流</span>\'}</div>',
    '                            </div>',
    '                            </div>',
    '                        </div>',
    '                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg p-3">',
    '                            <div>',
    '                                <label class="text-sm text-slate-300 font-medium"><i class="fas fa-random mr-1 text-cyan-400"></i>随机IP轮换</label>',
    '                                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-0.5">自动从免费代理源获取IP，每次注册换不同IP</p>',
    '                            </div>',
    '                            <label class="relative inline-flex items-center cursor-pointer">',
    '                                <input id="new-referral-proxy-enabled" type="checkbox" class="sr-only peer" ${task?.config?.referralProxyEnabled ? \'checked\' : \'\'} onchange="updateReferralProxyHint(this.checked)">',
    '                                <div class="w-11 h-6 bg-slate-600 peer-focus:outline-none rounded-full peer peer-checked:after:translate-x-full peer-checked:after:border-white after:content-[\'\'] after:absolute after:top-[2px] after:left-[2px] after:bg-white after:rounded-full after:h-5 after:w-5 after:transition-all peer-checked:bg-cyan-600"></div>',
    '                            </label>',
    '                        </div>',
    '                        <div class="bg-emerald-900/30 border border-emerald-500/30 rounded-xl p-3 space-y-1">',
    '                            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-400"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> 自动注册说明</p>',
    '                            <p class="text-xs text-emerald-300">• 自动检测面板类型（Vertos / VektalNodes / Laravel）</p>',
    '                            <p class="text-xs text-emerald-300">• 自动提取CSRF Token，自动生成用户名/姓名/邮箱/密码</p>',
    '                            <p class="text-xs text-emerald-300">• VektalNodes 自动生成指纹(fingerprint)绕过检测</p>',
    '                            <p class="text-xs text-emerald-300">• 开启随机IP轮换可有效避免429限流和IP封禁</p>',
    '                            <p class="text-xs text-emerald-300">• 用户名多种风格随机生成，更自然更隐蔽</p>',
    '                            <p class="text-xs text-emerald-300">• 开启IP轮换后无需设置注册间隔，代理切换本身需要时间，会自动连续注册</p>',
    '                        </div>',
